It fell out , therefore , that these two Earls joined their forces , took several of the Royal Castles in the country , and advanced as hard as they could on London . 
The London people , always opposed to the King , declared for them with great joy . 
The King himself remained shut up , not at all gloriously , in the Tower . 
Prince Edward made the best of his way to Windsor Castle . 
