Bruce parried the thrust , and with one blow of his battle axe split his skull . 
The Scottish men did not forget this , next day when the battle raged . 
But , they fought so well , and did such dreadful execution , that the English staggered . 
Then came Bruce himself upon them , with all the rest of his army . 
