He had also pledged himself that this Parliament should not be dissolved without its own consent until it had sat five months . 
When this Parliament met , Oliver made a speech to them of three hours long , very wisely advising them what to do for the credit and happiness of the country . 
Then he dismissed them to go to work . 
There was not at that time , in England or anywhere else , a man so able to govern the country as Oliver Cromwell . 
