Before we proceed to its principal events , let us dispose of Titus Oates . 
This fearful sentence was actually inflicted on the rascal . 
Being unable to stand after his first flogging , he was dragged on a sledge from Newgate to Tyburn , and flogged as he was drawn along . 
He was so strong a villain that he did not die under the torture , but lived to be afterwards pardoned and rewarded , though not to be ever believed in any more . 
